725183f-b.title: Queens: 30th Street - Broadway
725183f-b.text:
32-25 30th Street, east side, just south of Broadway,
showing the reay of the Sanford Mansion, which was purchased
by John E. Lockwood in 1864. The vantage point is 31st Street.
View 1:  Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  May, 1923
MAY BI REPRODUCED
View 2:  P. L Sperr  June 3, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS
